Titolo: Jackie Chan J-Mat Fitness

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: The Jackie Chan J-Mat Fitness is a mat serving as a video game requiring a XaviXPORT console to operate. This 2005 game, similar to the later released Nintendo game Wii Fit, is made to make players exercise. The players control Jackie Chan in a variety of modes such as reflex mode, running and exercising (which is played in a similar style to Dance Dance Revolution games).

Genere: Exergaming / Fitness 

Valutazione: N/A
